									<p>The speaker started to recap all the discussions since
										Day 1. How digital teaching and learning tools can be
										effective to learners. She taught us how to convert our
										traditional lesson plan into an E-learning plan. With the use
										of Google Drive, Google Classroom and any educational
										application that is available online. She also gave us our
										last group activity that will be presented on our 3rd day of
										seminar.</p>
									<p>On the afternoon, groups are planning and discussing on
										how we transform our traditional lesson plan into an E-
										learning lesson plan. Groups can choose either Blended or Full
										online Learning. It’s up to each group on how they would
